OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with patchy cloud and largely
OL,7,Fclear skies. Remaining dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight, leading to a touch
OL,9,Fof frost in more rural spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,12,Fspells. Remaining dry through the
OL,13,Fafternoon and turning cloudier later
OL,14,Fin south, but still some bright or
OL,15,Fsunny intervals breaking through.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
